sequenceDiagram
  participant Op as Operator
  participant Dev as Capture unit (stereo + LiDAR)
  participant Mob as Mobile app
  participant API as Cloud API
  participant Inf as Inference service (GPU)
  participant Grd as Grading service
  participant Str as Storage + Metadata DB
  participant MLOps

  Op->>Dev: trigger
  Dev->>Mob: RGB-D capture (RGB + LiDAR depth)
  Mob-->>API: upload over TLS
  API->>Inf: RGB-D patch
  Inf->>Grd: anomaly map + defect list
  Grd->>Str: write per-slab record + objects
  Grd-->>Mob: pass/fail + grade + heatmap
  API-->>MLOps: consented captures → DVC
  MLOps-->>Inf: new model image (cluster deploy)
